Agenda:

1) set up github repository first
2) create environment in project folder using below command
      conda create -p venv python==3.8 -y
    
3) create Readme file add,commit and push to github
4) create .gitignore in github and pull 
5) create requirements.txt file contains all required pacakages
6) create setup.py file that create as package for your project
7) Src folder create with __init__.py file
8) run command pip install -r requirements.txt
